<emphasis bold="true" box="[159,270,1869,1902]" pageId="155" pageNumber="434">Habitat.</emphasis>
Various Andean habitats from dry Pacific slopes to western margins of Altiplano at elevations of 1700-4000 m.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
